# 01-Templates

Reusable doc templates the PM workflow leans on. Hand-curated, not ingested.

`/12-ingest-knowledge` **never writes here.** It only reads the templates as reference scaffolds when proposing a new doc structure.

## What belongs here

- PRD outlines, kickoff one-pager skeletons, persona-card blanks, market-brief skeletons, retro templates
- Anything a human pre-defines as the "shape" of a recurring doc type

## Schema

Free-form. Templates are starting points, not structured data. Name files `<doc-type>.md.template`.
